樟宜机场地铁站現有東西線樟宜機場支線提供來往該站與丹那美拉地鐵站與穿梭列車服務<ref name="LTA system map">{{Cite web|url=https://www.lta.gov.sg/content/dam/ltagov/getting_around/public_transport/rail_network/pdf/sm-20-03-en-exp.pdf|title=MRT System Map|last=|first=|date=|website=LTA|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821064838/https://www.lta.gov.sg/content/dam/ltagov/getting_around/public_transport/rail_network/pdf/sm-20-03-en-exp.pdf|archive-date=2020-08-21|access-date=}}</ref>。樟宜機場地鐵站於2002年2月8日對外開放後，初期有來往該站與[[文禮地鐵站|文禮地鐵站]]的直通運行服務<ref>{{Cite news|title=Boon Lay to Expo: MRT now running|date=2001-12-20|work=The Straits Times}}</ref>，惟後來因客量低下而於2003年7月22日起停止服務，並改為來往該站與丹那美拉地鐵站與穿梭列車服務<ref name="18jul2003">{{Cite news|title=Board MRT to airport from Tanah Merah.|date=2003-07-18|work=The Straits Times}}</ref>。自樟宜機場地鐵站至丹那美拉地鐵站的首班車在星期一至六於05:31開出，而在星期日及法定假日於05:59開出，至於末班車則於翌日00:06開出<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://journey.smrt.com.sg/journey/station_info/changi-airport/first-and-last-train/|title=SMRT Journeys (First and last trains from Changi Airport)|website=journey.smrt.com.sg|access-date=2020-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190914142639/http://journey.smrt.com.sg/journey/station_info/changi-airport/first-and-last-train/|archive-date=2019-09-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。自丹那美拉地鐵站至樟宜機場地鐵站的首班車在星期一至六於05:20開出，而在星期日及法定假日於05:47開出，至於末班車則於23:50開出<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://journey.smrt.com.sg/journey/station_info/tanah-merah/first-and-last-train/|title=SMRT Journeys (First and last trains from Tanah Merah)|website=journey.smrt.com.sg|access-date=2020-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190904061858/http://journey.smrt.com.sg/journey/station_info/tanah-merah/first-and-last-train|archive-date=2019-09-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Singapore Changi Airport">{{cite web | title=Getting to the Airport | website=Singapore Changi Airport | url=https://www.changiairport.com/en/airport-guide/transport/getting-to-the-airport.html#anchorTrain | access-date=2020-04-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190908091717/http://www.changiairport.com/en/airport-guide/transport/getting-to-the-airport.html#anchorTrain | archive-date=2019-09-08 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。列車[[班距|班距]]在繁忙時間約為7至9分鐘一班，而在非繁忙時間則為12分鐘一班<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://landtransportguru.net/changi-airport-station/|title=Changi Airport MRT Station {{!}} Land Transport Guru|date=2018-01-31|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180620015233/http://landtransportguru.net/changi-airport-station/|archive-date=2018-06-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="TODAYonline 2014">{{cite web | title=Tanah Merah station to get new tracks, platform | website=TODAYonline | date=2014-08-26 | url=https://www.todayonline.com/singapore/tanah-merah-station-get-new-tracks-platform | access-date=2020-04-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140831002908/http://www.todayonline.com/singapore/tanah-merah-station-get-new-tracks-platform | archive-date=2014-08-31 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.smrttrains.com.sg/Journey-with-Us/Travel-Information/Visiting-Singapore|title=Visiting Singapore|website=www.smrttrains.com.sg|access-date=2020-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200203154723/http://www.smrttrains.com.sg/Journey-with-Us/Travel-Information/Visiting-Singapore|archive-date=2020-02-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

樟宜機場地鐵站的編號原為“EW29”<ref>{{cite news |last1=Salim |first1=Shazalina |title=Red, green and grey |url=https://eresources.nlb.gov.sg/newspapers/Digitised/Article/today20010803-1.2.16.1 |date=2001-08-03 |pages=9 |accessdate=2020-09-30 |archive-date=2020-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030025643/https://eresources.nlb.gov.sg/newspapers/Digitised/Article/today20010803-1.2.16.1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，後於2003年6月20日改為“CG2”<ref>{{Cite news|last=|first=|url=https://eresources.nlb.gov.sg/newspapers/Digitised/Search?ST=1&AT=advanced&K=Changi%20Airport%20Station&KA=Changi%20Airport%20Station&DF=01%2F04%2F2001&DT=01%2F08%2F2003&Display=0&NPT=&L=&CTA=Article#|title=What SMRT said earlier|date=2001-08-08|work=The New Paper|access-date=|dead-url=no|archive-date=2020-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821064820/https://eresources.nlb.gov.sg/newspapers/Digitised/Search?ST=1&AT=advanced&K=Changi+Airport+Station&KA=Changi+Airport+Station&DF=01%2F04%2F2001&DT=01%2F08%2F2003&Display=0&NPT=&L=&CTA=Article}}</ref>。2040年，樟宜機場支線將劃入湯申－東海岸線的機場延線，而在樟宜機場支線上的樟宜機場地鐵站亦將成為湯申－東海岸線的地鐵站<ref name="LTMP 2040"/>。

===設計===
[[File:Changi_Airport_MRT_Station_(EWL_-_Changi_Branch)_-_Exit_A.jpg|thumb]]
樟宜機場地鐵站的設計中融入了不同的元素，使之更具美感<ref name="Speech 1"/>。樟宜機場地鐵站由[[SOM建築設計事務所|SOM建築設計事務所]]設計，內部空間寬敞，島式月台上方有一條{{convert|150|m|ft}}長的連通橋<ref name="alpha">{{Cite book|last=Goh|first=Sushma|title=RE:think – Designing For Wayfinding|publisher=Land Transport Authority|year=2018|isbn=|location=|pages=25}}</ref>。該連通橋連接樟宜機場2號及3號客運大樓<ref name="beta"/>，除了有燈光照明外<ref name="alpha"/>，也附設[[電動步道|電動步道]]<ref name="beta">{{Cite web|url=https://www.sgtrains.com/network-ewl.html#CG2|title=East-West Line|website=SGTrains|access-date=2020-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180523075407/http://www.sgtrains.com/network-ewl.html#CG2|archive-date=2018-05-23|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="bootsnail">{{Cite web|url=https://www.bootsnall.com/articles/15-of-the-coolest-subway-stops-in-the-world.html|title=15 of the Most Beautiful Subway Stops in the World – BootsnAll Travel Articles|access-date=2019-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517115407/https://www.bootsnall.com/articles/15-of-the-coolest-subway-stops-in-the-world.html|archive-date=2019-05-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]工程公司邁進外牆工程設計（{{lang|en|Meinhardt Facades}}）則負責玻璃幕牆與中庭內兩個在站體兩端旁、靠近樟宜機場2號及3號客運大樓的{{link-en|抗拉結構|Tensile structure}}{{notetag|每個抗拉結構約{{convert|60|m|ft}}長、{{convert|20|m|ft}}寬、{{convert|36|m|ft}}高。<ref name="gamma"/>}}的結構設計工程，而[[奧雅納|奧雅納]]也有參與到其中工程設計<ref name="gamma">{{Cite web|url=https://www.meinhardt.com.sg/projects/changi-airport-glass-atria/|title=Changi Airport Glass Atria {{!}} Meinhardt – Transforming Cities, Shaping the Future|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190906204400/http://www.meinhardt.com.sg/projects/changi-airport-glass-atria/|archive-date=2019-09-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://andreamignini.com/03-MENU-METRO/images/singapore/Singapore%20Changi%20Airport%20MRT%20Station%20Design%20&%20Construction%20of%20Glass%20Atria.pdf|title=Singapore Changi Airport MRT Station Design & Construction of Glass Atria|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-20|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030025641/http://andreamignini.com/03-MENU-METRO/images/singapore/Singapore%20Changi%20Airport%20MRT%20Station%20Design%20%26%20Construction%20of%20Glass%20Atria.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年，樟宜機場地鐵站被BootsnAll評為全球15個最美麗的地鐵站中的第10名<ref name="bootsnail"/>。
